    <h1>About XA</h1>
    <p>XA is South Africa's only full service international trade consulting firm focusing on both trade policy matters as well as customs and excise matters.  The result is a completely integrated solution to the international trade challenges facing companies that trade across the world.</p>
    <p>In order to provide a complete and integrated solution, XA's approach to our clients is different to the approach of our competitors.  We look at your complete international trade profile, from the duties you pay on your inputs, to the duty protection you have on the products you sell.  We consider the trade compliance issues for every step in your supply chain and then look at ways to optimise this supply chain.</p>
    <p>Our unique methodology allows us to deliver superb results for our clients, as can be confirmed by simply talking to any of our existing clients.  References can be provided if required.</p>

    <h1>The XA Team</h1>
    <p>Our unique way of working has resulted in us employing some very special people.  The XA team is not only well qualified and experienced, but also passionate about international trade.  The end result is not only a team who knows what they are doing, but a team who approaches each project with enthusiasm.</p>
